<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Ana Luísa - Portfólio de Dados</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 { font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4CAF50;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .content { padding: 40px; }
        .about {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 5px solid #667eea;
        }
        .about h2 { color: #333; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .links-section { margin: 30px 0; }
        .links-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            display: block;
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .card .emoji { font-size: 3em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .tech-section { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .tech-items {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .tech-item {
            background: #e0e7ff;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            color: #4c51bf;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .header h1 { font-size: 1.8em; }
            .content { padding: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Ana Luísa Vieira Borges</h1>
            <p>Ciência de Dados & Machine Learning</p>
            <div class="badge">🎓 Bootcamp I - 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="about">
                <h2>📌 Sobre mim</h2>
                <p>Estudante de Ciência de Dados, apaixonada por transformar dados em insights. Este é meu portfólio profissional integrado com IA Gemini.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="links-section">
                <h2>📂 Meus materiais</h2>
                <div class="card-grid">
                    <a href="#" class="card">
                        <span class="emoji">📑</span>
                        <h3>Relatório</h3>
                        <p>Documentação completa do projeto</p>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="card">
                        <span class="emoji">📊</span>
                        <h3>Slides</h3>
                        <p>Apresentação visual para a banca</p>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/analuborges3784-ops" target="_blank" class="card">
                        <span class="emoji">💻</span>
                        <h3>GitHub</h3>
                        <p>Todo o código do projeto</p>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ana-lu%C3%ADsa-vieira-borges-6b7813402" target="_blank" class="card">
                        <span class="emoji">🔗</span>
                        <h3>LinkedIn</h3>
                        <p>Meu perfil profissional</p>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-section">
                <h2>🛠️ Tecnologias</h2>
                <div class="tech-items">
                    <span class="tech-item">Python</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">Git & GitHub</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">GitHub Pages</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">IA - Gemini</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2026 Ana Luísa Vieira Borges | Portfólio sob licença MIT</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
